stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> queued: POST /api/scan (another scan active)
    [*] --> pending: POST /api/scan (no active scan)
    queued --> pending: prior scan terminal, _start_next_queued()
    queued --> [*]: DELETE /api/scan/{id}

    pending --> scanning: run_scan_pipeline starts
    scanning --> metadata: discover_videos done
    metadata --> hashing: stage 2 done
    hashing --> comparing: stage 3 done

    scanning --> paused: POST /scan/{id}/pause
    metadata --> paused: POST /scan/{id}/pause
    hashing --> paused: POST /scan/{id}/pause
    comparing --> paused: POST /scan/{id}/pause
    paused --> scanning: POST /scan/{id}/resume

    comparing --> completed: pipeline ok
    scanning --> failed: exception
    metadata --> failed: exception
    hashing --> failed: exception
    comparing --> failed: exception

    scanning --> stopped: POST /scan/{id}/stop
    metadata --> stopped: POST /scan/{id}/stop
    hashing --> stopped: POST /scan/{id}/stop
    comparing --> stopped: POST /scan/{id}/stop
    paused --> stopped: POST /scan/{id}/stop

    pending --> stopped: server restart (_recover_orphaned_scans)
    scanning --> stopped: server restart
    metadata --> stopped: server restart
    hashing --> stopped: server restart
    comparing --> stopped: server restart
    paused --> stopped: server restart

    completed --> [*]: DELETE /api/scan/{id}
    failed --> [*]: DELETE /api/scan/{id}
    stopped --> [*]: DELETE /api/scan/{id}
